data.description: PRICE REDUCED!! BUY THIS HOME w/Last Year's Interest Rate!! 5.5% Fixed Rate Assumable Loan! 4 BR 3 BA Modern Farmhouse on 5.28 AC Lot minutes from Downtown Areas in Plainfield & Mooresville w/gorgeous views of White Lick Creek! Main floor has natural light from skylights, vaulted ceiling in spacious great room/relax in the warmth by the wood burning fireplace. Large kitchen w adjoining sunroom is perfect to enjoy morning coffee. Experience comfort/relaxation of your own personal retreat in primary bedroom w balcony/private bath featuring large garden tub. Fully finished basement w wood burning fireplace & stunning stone wall/glass doors leading to balcony & deck. Home is minutes from shops/eateries. Schedule your tour today!
